---
import ScrollAnimation from './ScrollAnimation.jsx';
import '../styles/contact.css';
---

<section id="contacto" class="contact-section">
    <div class="contact-inner">
        <ScrollAnimation className="contact-info" delay={0.2} client:load as="div">
            <span class="contact-badge">Tu turno</span>
            <h2 class="contact-title">Esta historia la escribimos juntos</h2>
            <p class="contact-description">
                No importa si apenas estás empezando o si ya llevas años en tecnología. Lo que importa es que creas que Chitagá merece más. Cada persona que se suma fortalece esta comunidad. Tu voz, tu idea, tu ganas de aprender: eso es lo que nos hace falta.
            </p>
            <div class="contact-socials">
                <a href="#" class="social-link" aria-label="Facebook">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                        <path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/>
                    </svg>
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="social-link" aria-label="Instagram">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                        <path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zM12 0C8.741 0 8.333.014 7.053.072 2.695.272.273 2.69.073 7.052.014 8.333 0 8.741 0 12c0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98C8.333 23.986 8.741 24 12 24c3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98C15.668.014 15.259 0 12 0zm0 5.838a6.162 6.162 0 100 12.324 6.162 6.162 0 000-12.324zM12 16a4 4 0 110-8 4 4 0 010 8zm6.406-11.845a1.44 1.44 0 100 2.881 1.44 1.44 0 000-2.881z"/>
                    </svg>
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="social-link" aria-label="GitHub">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                        <path d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
                    </svg>
                </a>
            </div>
        </ScrollAnimation>

        <form id="contact-form" class="contact-form">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="contact-name">Nombre</label>
                <input type="text" id="contact-name" name="name" placeholder="Tu nombre" />
                <span id="name-status" class="field-status"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="contact-email">Correo electrónico</label>
                <input type="email" id="contact-email" name="email" placeholder="tu@correo.com" />
                <span id="email-status" class="field-status"></span>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="contact-message">Mensaje</label>
                <textarea id="contact-message" name="message" rows="4" placeholder="Cuéntanos por qué quieres ser parte (mín. 20 caracteres)"></textarea>
                <span id="message-status" class="field-status"></span>
            </div>
            <button type="button" id="contact-submit-btn" class="contact-submit">Quiero ser parte</button>
            <p id="form-feedback" class="form-feedback"></p>
        </form>
    </div>

    <!-- Success popup -->
    <div id="success-popup" class="popup-overlay">
        <div class="popup-card">
            <div class="popup-icon">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="popup-title">Ya eres parte de esto</h3>
            <p class="popup-text">Gracias por creer en Chitagá. Pronto nos pondremos en contacto contigo para dar el siguiente paso juntos.</p>
            <button type="button" id="popup-close" class="popup-btn">Entendido</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script is:inline src="/scripts/contact-form.js"></script>
</section>
